data.description: ASK ABOUT THE $8,500 IN BUYER'S CLOSING COSTS/PREPAIDS OR BUY DOWNS! STUNNING 4 BEDROOM 2 BATH HOME THAT SITS ON OVER AN ACRE OF LAND, offering a serene country living atmosphere while being conveniently close to city amenities. This spacious open concept features a striking stack stone fireplace and vaulted ceilings in the living room, complemented by beautiful wood-like tile throughout the common areas. The kitchen boasts a huge island perfect for entertaining, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a generous pantry. The master suite, taking up the entire west side of the home, includes an accent wall for easy decorating, a magnificent tray ceiling, a luxurious master bathroom with his and her sinks, a jetted whirlpool tub and a separate shower, as well as a master closet the size of an office or study. The patio provides an ideal space for hosting guests, especially in the spring and summer, and there's plenty of land to accommodate a pool or shop. Additionally, the property features a huge three-car garage and ample parking. Enjoy peace and security in this tight nit community located in a quiet cul-de-sac. Bridgecreek or Blanchard schools! Your choice! Ask about incentives! Come be a part of the amazing Sandstone Ridge community. Schedule your own private showing today!
